Such a function might be written as:

```
function im($imgName) {
    $pathToImgs = &quot;images/&quot;;
    if (file_exists( $pathToImgs . $imgName )) {
        echo $pathToImgs . $imgName;
    }
    else {
        echo $pathToImgs . &quot;placeholder.jpg&quot;;
    }
}
```

